OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with patchy
OL,6,Frain. This afternoon will be mainly
OL,7,Fdry and cloudy across the south, but
OL,8,Ffurther spells of rain across Argyll.
OL,9,FBrisk westerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith rain across Argyll, drier
OL,13,Felsewhere. Then the rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill be cloudy with some patchy rain,
OL,15,Ffar south drier.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with some
OL,18,Fpatchy rain, this becoming confined to
OL,19,Fthe Argyll during the afternoon.
OL,20,FChance of a little brightness in the
OL,21,Fafternoon in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
