OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart on Wednesday with drizzly rain
OL,7,Facross Argyll, otherwise dry and
OL,8,Fbrightening up by afternoon. Thursday
OL,9,Fand Friday dry and very warm with some
OL,10,Fbrightness.
